We increased the number of electric vehicles to around 4,100 and charging points to around 2,750 in fiscal 2023.

In the UK, we have already made a lot of progress in creating an exclusively electric vehicle fleet. As a result, 23% of the company fleet is now all-electric, and electric vehicles accounted for 44% of all new car orders at the end of fiscal 2023.

